  <h1>About everydaymoneylab</h1>
  <p>everydaymoneylab is a personal finance publication built for people who want honest, practical guidance without the hustle-culture theatrics — including a dedicated focus on halal personal finance for readers who need money advice that actually respects their principles instead of ignoring them.</p>
  <p>No affiliate-stuffed "best credit cards" lists. No pretending interest-based products don't matter. Just clear breakdowns of how to save, invest, and plan — written by someone who's rebuilding his own financial footing from the ground up, not selling a course about it.</p>
  <p>Written by Hussain J.</p>
</article>
